g", "notes": "Activity fee 150 + basketball 200 + supplies 87 + sports physical 30. Getting receipts from Claudia."}, "created_time": "2026-02-06T03:00:00Z", "modified_time": "2026-02-06T03:00:00Z"}, {"id": "recfa74acbafcda01fd", "table_id": "tbl6a9c3e5f7d1b28a", "fields": {"category": "Tax", "item": "Orthodontist payments 2025", "amount": 2100.0, "due_date": "2026-04-15", "status": "pending", "notes": "12 x 175 to Peninsula Ortho. Medical deduction threshold is 7.5% of AGI. At 48k thats $3600. Probably cant deduct unless I add other medical."}, "created_time": "2026-02-06T03:00:00Z", "modified_time": "2026-02-06T03:00:00Z"}, {"id": "rec1f5cfba9b05be74a", "table_id": "tbl6a9c3e5f7d1b28a", "fields": {"category": "Tax", "item": "TurboTax free filing", "amount": 0.0, "due_date": "2026-03-12", "status": "completed", "notes": "Filed federal + CA state electronically Mar 12. Expecting ~$500 total refund. Free filing for simple return."}, "created_time": "2026-03-13T03:30:00Z", "modified_time": "2026-03-13T03:30:00Z"}, {"id": "recea76dc0975c5d00b", "table_id": "tbl7c117effb6a910e0", "fields": {"project_name": "ML Environment Setup", "status": "complete", "description": "Set up Python ML dev environment. Installed Python 3.11, virtualenv, jupyter, numpy, pandas, scikit-learn, matplotlib.", "last_updated": "2026-01-18", "tags": "setup, python, ml", "notes": "Using Homebrew on Mac. Terrence helped with the virtualenv config."}, "created_time": "2026-01-18T23:00:00Z", "modified_time": "2026-01-18T23:00:00Z"}, {"id": "rec2e856d4e6ff2fe25", "table_id": "tbl7c117effb6a910e0", "fields": {"project_name": "Coursera ML Specialization", "status": "in progress", "description": "Andrew Ng's Machine Learning Specialization on Coursera. Three courses: supervised learning, advanced algorithms, unsupervised learning.", "last_updated": "2026-02-15", "tags": "coursera, education, ml", "notes": "Week 1 done Jan 25. Linear regression and classification basics. The gradient descent stuff finally