T code", "priority": "high", "notes": "Highest complexity. Need to verify CPT codes against procedure description. Pre-auth required for most.", "example_text": "Patient underwent laparoscopic cholecystectomy with general anesthesia. Procedure time 45 minutes. Overnight observation."}, "created_time": "2026-02-15T20:00:00Z", "modified_time": "2026-02-15T20:00:00Z"}, {"id": "recf9644b45552b3f99", "table_id": "tblc4aee3a3dc201c3a", "fields": {"category": "Pharmacy", "claim_type": "outpatient", "keywords": "prescription, medication, refill, formulary, prior auth, generic, brand", "priority": "medium", "notes": "Check formulary status. Generics vs brand name. Prior auth for non-formulary items.", "example_text": "Rx filled: Amoxicillin 500mg, 30 day supply. Generic substitution applied."}, "created_time": "2026-02-15T20:00:00Z", "modified_time": "2026-02-15T20:00:00Z"}, {"id": "rec45cc166c16fe6421", "table_id": "tblc4aee3a3dc201c3a", "fields": {"category": "Durable Medical Equipment", "claim_type": "outpatient", "keywords": "wheelchair, oxygen, CPAP, brace, equipment rental, DME supplier", "priority": "medium", "notes": "Duration of need matters. Rental vs purchase thresholds. Check supplier network status.", "example_text": "CPAP machine rental, 3 month initial period, supplier: MedEquip Inc. Monthly rental $180."}, "created_time": "2026-02-15T20:00:00Z", "modified_time": "2026-02-15T20:00:00Z"}, {"id": "rec7a397fb03136f709", "table_id": "tblc4aee3a3dc201c3a", "fields": {"category": "Provider Refund", "claim_type": "adjustment", "keywords": "refund, overpayment, duplicate, resubmission, correction, billing pattern", "priority": "high", "notes": "Secondary review trigger. Watch for billing pattern anomalies. Multiple refund requests from same provider = flag.", "example_text": "Provider requesting refund of $1,200 overpayment on claim dated 10/15. Third refund request in 90 days."}, "created_time": "2026-02-15T20:00:00Z", "modified_time": "2026-02-15T20:00:00Z"}, {"id": "rec8cd4afb36696172b", "table_id": "tblc4aee3a3dc201c3a", "fields": {"category": "Diagnostic/Lab", "claim_type": "outpatient", "keywords": "lab work, blood test, imaging, MRI, CT scan, X-ray, pathology", "priority": "low", "notes": "Usually straightforward. Watch for bundling violations and duplicate orders.", "example_text": "Routine blood panel: CBC, CMP, lipid panel, A1C. Quest Diagnostics. Ordered by PCP."}, "created_time": "2026-02-15T20:00:00Z", "modified_time": "2026-02-15T20:00:00Z"}]}